snippet.title: Engage Souls - Release Gameplay - Mobile - F2P - JP
snippet.description:
Here is a new mobile game using Unreal Engine 4 by Square Enix. The combat is turn-based with a rock, paper, scissors system and some kind of pets or summons. Looks like pokemon game with jojo stands :P

Game website: https://www.jp.square-enix.com/engagesouls/
Official twitter: https://twitter.com/EnSol_PR
Official facebook: https://www.facebook.com/EnSolPR

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.square_enix.android_googleplay.engagesouls
Apk download: https://apps.qoo-app.com/en/app/10627
iOS: https://apps.apple.com/jp/app/%E3%82%A8%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B2%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B8%E3%82%BD%E3%82%A6%E3%83%AB%E3%82%BA/id1488741024

Note: Running on Shield TV, could not make it run on emulator.

#EngageSouls #エンゲージソウルズ
